Harvest component of salmon operating model

Source: R/Harvest_MMP.R
make_Harvest_MMP.Rd

A function that creates a multi-stock management procedure

Usage

make_Harvest_MMP(u_terminal = 0.1, u_preterminal = 0, m = 0, release_mort = 0)

Arguments

u_terminal

Numeric between 0-1. Harvest rate of the terminal fishery.

u_preterminal

Numeric between 0-1. Harvest rate of the preterminal fishery.

m

Numeric between 0-1. Mark rate, i.e., retention rate.

release_mort

Vector length 2 (each numeric between 0-1). Release mortality, proportion of released fish that die.
